checklist because if you\u2019re not implementing long-tails, you&#8217;re missing out on high-intent, low-cost traffic that could be yours.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Ad Text Optimization<\/strong> \u2013 The PPC audit reviews your <a href=\"\/text-ads\">text ad<\/a> usage because your <a href=\"\/ad-text\">ad text<\/a> greatly affects your impressions, clicks, CTR and ad ranking.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Landing Page Optimization<\/strong> \u2013 Generally, the more landing pages you have, the more targeted your messaging can be. The <strong>PPC campaign audit<\/strong> makes sure you have enough <a href=\"\/landing-page-optimization\">landing pages<\/a> to match up against competitors.<\/li>\n<li><strong>PPC Best Practices<\/strong> \u2013 Our PPC audit checklist includes a list of proven best practices that <a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2012\/03\/14\/ppc-bid-management-guide\">PPC experts<\/a> follow for superior PPC performance.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>WordStream&#8217;s Google Ads Performance Grader offers advertisers control over every aspect of their PPC account management from a single, intuitive dashboard interface. In addition, our comprehensive PPC audits also offer guidance on how to use advanced features such as Expanded Text Ads, as well as how to optimize your campaign to target mobile traffic.<\/p>\n<div data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"422dc2a5-841d-4335-9ffa-ec1beb88b588\" data-langcode=\"und\" class=\"embedded-entity align-center\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/adwords-performance-grader-mobile-advertising-optimization-5.png\" width=\"1048\" height=\"720\" alt=\"AdWords Performance Grader PPC Audit mobile advertising optimization report\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p>Other PPC audit programs don\u2019t provide the full details of what improvements should be made, but 